{"tid":1776011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周末拘42人 涉嫌暴動、藏有攻擊性武器、無牌藏有槍械、串謀傷人等","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T09:17:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"17e553a63b5d1e6dc6431e26c267703eba35060f","tid":1776011,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"警方舉行記者會，表示周末共拘捕42人，包括37男5女，年齡介乎14至63歲，涉嫌參與暴動、藏有攻擊性武器、無牌藏有槍械、串謀傷人等。<br />\n<br />\n警方並表示，六月至今的總拘捕人數為6022人，包括4474男1548女，年齡介乎11至84歲，主要涉參與非法集結、參與暴動、藏有攻擊性武器等。當中有2393人為學生，佔總拘捕人數四成。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過去半年，警方曾使用約16000發催淚彈、約10000發橡膠彈、約2000發布袋彈及約1850發海綿彈。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9cb71cae06040632e80d0cb3569c338af8eb73d6","tid":1776011,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"班狗根本就係喺度自編自導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af593073aa2fd7f9bb49c8f49f83167139f6a4c","tid":1776011,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"平均每人要用2粒催淚彈+2粒防暴子彈<br />\n先可以拘捕佢地<br />\n手足係iron man<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354653c97b32887f539e2848a188fafaf4ee400f","tid":1776011,"uid":306621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:30:48.000Z","msg":"參與暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日係暴動現場?"},{"pid":"b2b1c9570c14c7eaf1b59593dd44c3a5503750d2","tid":1776011,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"354653c97b32887f539e2848a188